data.description: Affordable acreage right off a paved road! Make this place your own, 3 bed 1.5 baths, and open kitchen on the main floor, large walkout basement with finished living area and 3 other rooms that would be perfect for storage, an office, or could be made into a bedroom with an egress window. Large 2 car garage, no covenants and all on over 2 acres!
